nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 182 is the 160th issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the 90th issue published by Titan Magazines. It was published on July 10, 2018.
Star Wars Insider #182 takes a sneak peek at what to expect from Disney Park's Star Wars Galaxy's Edge, and takes a look at some of the best Star Wars childrens books ever published.
Plus, all the latest movie, TV, and merchandise news!
